						<summary>

						<p>On the base of the main <hi rend="italic">gōpura,</hi> west side, proper right of entrance.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1780, Śubhakṛit, Bhādrapada śu. 15.</hi> Irregular.</p>						

						<p>It records the gift of ten rupees per year by Peda Narasaya and Pina Narasaya sons of Narasayya for burning lamps in front of god Rāmasvāmi.</p>						

